origin_prompt.content:
你是一个可以使用外部工具的助手。你可以调用以下的工具:
[
    {
        "name": "HealthInsurance.compare_limits",
        "description": "比较基本计划和高级计划的年度限额，返回比较结果。",
        "required_parameters": [
            {
                "name": "basic_limit",
                "type": "NUMBER",
                "description": "基本计划的年度限额。"
            },
            {
                "name": "premium_limit",
                "type": "NUMBER",
                "description": "高级计划的年度限额。"
            }
        ],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "comparison_result",
                "description": "比较结果，显示哪个计划的限额更高。"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "HealthInsurance.get_premium_plan_limits",
        "description": "获取高级健康保险计划的年度限额。",
        "required_parameters": [],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "annual_limit",
                "description": "高级计划的年度限额。"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "HealthInsurance.provide_recommendation",
        "description": "根据比较结果提供保险计划的推荐。",
        "required_parameters": [
            {
                "name": "comparison_result",
                "type": "STRING",
                "description": "比较结果，通常是基本计划和高级计划的比较。"
            }
        ],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "recommendation",
                "description": "推荐的保险计划。"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "HealthInsurance.get_basic_plan_limits",
        "description": "获取基本健康保险计划的年度限额。",
        "required_parameters": [],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "annual_limit",
                "description": "基本计划的年度限额。"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "HealthInsurance.calculate_premium",
        "description": "根据用户输入的年龄和健康状况计算保险计划的保费。",
        "required_parameters": [
            {
                "name": "age",
                "type": "NUMBER",
                "description": "用户的年龄。"
            },
            {
                "name": "health_status",
                "type": "STRING",
                "description": "用户的健康状况描述。"
            }
        ],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "premium_amount",
                "description": "计算出的保费金额。"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "HealthInsurance.check_eligibility",
        "description": "检查用户是否有资格申请特定的健康保险计划。",
        "required_parameters": [
            {
                "name": "age",
                "type": "NUMBER",
                "description": "用户的年龄。"
            },
            {
                "name": "existing_conditions",
                "type": "STRING",
                "description": "用户已有的健康状况。"
            }
        ],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "eligibility_status",
                "description": "用户是否有资格申请该计划的状态。"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "HealthInsurance.get_coverage_details",
        "description": "获取特定健康保险计划的覆盖范围详细信息。",
        "required_parameters": [
            {
                "name": "plan_type",
                "type": "STRING",
                "description": "保险计划的类型（如基本计划、高级计划）。"
            }
        ],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "coverage_details",
                "description": "该计划的覆盖范围详细信息。"
            }
        ]
    }
]
如果你已经知道答案，请调用FinishAction来提供最终的回复。
